# Design Mockups and SVG Assets

Mockups (`MCK-##`) in `mockups.md`; journeys (`JRN-##`) in `user-journeys.md`.

**Upstream first:** No new screen/SVG without trace to `F##`, `FR-F##-##`, and (when applicable) `JRN-##`. Update `mockups.md` and `library.md` before adding assets.

**Architecture gate:** Before creating or materially updating `db-and-dfd.md`, pass [Ready checklist](04-solution-strategy.mdc#ready-checklist) in [04-solution-strategy.mdc](04-solution-strategy.mdc) and ensure `building-blocks.md` is current.

## Asset layout

```
4-design/
├── library.md, mockups.md, user-journeys.md
└── mockups/
    ├── screens/     MCK-##-kebab-slug.svg
    ├── journeys/    JRN-##-kebab-slug.svg (optional)
    └── components/  CMP-##-kebab-slug.svg (optional)
```

## Naming

- Filename starts with `MCK-##` / `JRN-##` / `CMP-##`; kebab slug matches `mockups.md` anchor
- One canonical SVG per `MCK-##` unless explicit variant (e.g. `-phone`)
- No orphans — every asset has index row + markdown section

## SVG authoring

| Rule | Requirement |
|------|-------------|
| XML | `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>` first line |
| Root | `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 W H">` — reuse frame (e.g. 360×780) |
| Non-ASCII | XML numeric entities (e.g. `&#1041;`) |
| No emoji | Shapes or ASCII in `<text>` |
| Escapes | `&` → `&amp;`, `<` → `&lt;` in text nodes |
| Tokens | Match `library.md` |
| A11y | `<title>`, `<desc>`, `role="img"`, `aria-labelledby` when appropriate |

## Wiring

| Location | Add |
|----------|-----|
| `mockups.md` index | **File** column link to SVG |
| Each `MCK-##` section | `![…](mockups/screens/…svg)` + **Layout** bullets |
| `user-journeys.md` | **Visual flow** — storyboard and/or step embeds |
| Feature **UI flow** | Link to `../4-design/mockups.md#anchor` |
| `library.md` | Screen inventory links |

Mermaid `journey` = satisfaction/emotion; SVG = layout/navigation. Use both.

## When to add or update

1. Spec first — **Layout (planned)** and trace rows in `mockups.md`
2. MVP paths on primary journeys first
3. Defer vNext screens until scope active
4. Propagate token/layout changes to `library.md`, SVGs, journeys, feature UI links in one pass
5. New `MCK-##` row + `CMP-##` in `library.md` before creating SVG

Validate per [09-validation-open-questions.mdc](09-validation-open-questions.mdc) mockup items.
